  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Cook",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are hiring at our Holland Village and Tanglin Mall locations.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We’re looking for a <strong>reliable, efficient, and passionate Cook</strong> to join our kitchen team! If you enjoy working with fresh ingredients, preparing honest and delicious food, and being part of a supportive team, we’d love to hear from you.  We make our bread and desserts on site as well as our pasta, sauces and soups.  You can see our menu online.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and cook a variety of dishes according to established recipes and standards</li>\n  <li>Ensure food quality, presentation, and consistency</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene in the kitchen at all times</li>\n  <li>Assist with food prep, stock taking, and kitchen organisation</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the team to ensure smooth and timely service</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Previous kitchen experience</li>\n  <li>Good understanding of food hygiene and safety</li>\n  <li>Ability to work quickly and efficiently under pressure</li>\n  <li>Team player with a positive attitude</li>\n  <li>Willingness to learn and follow kitchen procedures and recipes to prepare menu items of a consistent quality</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive salary and daily staff meals</li>\n  <li>Training and growth opportunities</li>\n  <li>Supportive team and stable work environment</li>\n  <li>Exposure to fresh, preservative-free food and a wholesome menu</li>\n</ul>",
